3298.Name: Men's Tuned Up Tournament 10+ PTI
3298.Details:
When: October 9th
Where: Wildwood GC & North Park
Cost: $130/Team
Start time: First matches begin at 8:30 AM

Sign up for the annual Tuned Up Tournament. This year, the tournament will be a Men's tournament for players with a PTI of 10 or higher. The field will consist of 32 teams. You should enter as a team. The cost covers balls, lunch, water, adult beverages, favor, prizes, and courts. Three matches are guaranteed, weather permitting. 

We will split the tournament into two flights based on the participants.

For questions, reach out to contact@pghpaddle.com. 

We'll see you on the courts!
3298.RegistrationDetails: $130 per team. All registrations must be received by 10/4/21. All participants must be 21 or older. The tournament will be ranked and seeded by combined team PTI. If there is a large disparity in PTI we may break the tournament into two separate PTI flights.
